Four Liberties vs Three Liberties?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b Black to play\b0 .
\par Black has three liberties white White has 4.
\par At first it seems Black can't win this capturing race.
\par
\par However White's position has a defect. Black can create shortage of liberties and win the capturing race.
\par
\par
\par }
